title: Ron Wyatt. Discovered Series 04 Of 05. The Exodus
description: Exodus - Red Sea - Mt. Sinai - More. This comprehensive video explores the events & route of the Exodus, revealing the extensive amount of evidence which proves the precise accuracy of the Biblical account in thrilling detail. It features the Red Sea Crossing site and Mt. Sinai in Saudi Arabia. Also included is a bonus feature on How the Pyramids were built.
